column1: 597387427444039680:::Sun May 10 13:07:16 +0000 2015:::Perrrty view last night at the footy #aflsunscrows #gocrows https://t.co/M1huixOHoN:::None
597369063296237568:::Sun May 10 11:54:17 +0000 2015:::RT @SAfooty_: FT: @Adelaide_FC 18.11 (119) d @GoldCoastSUNS 11.12 (78) Betts finished with five. Tex had four. #AFLSunsCrows:::None
597278026213109760:::Sun May 10 05:52:32 +0000 2015:::@liamthompson1 Getting to the ground is a nightmare - be VERY difficult if s full house! #AFLSunsCrows:::None
597276990341689345:::Sun May 10 05:48:26 +0000 2015:::And lack of people at ground last night. Heavy Crows following. Queensland footy definitely needs some work. #AFLSunsCrows:::None
597276820023545857:::Sun May 10 05:47:45 +0000 2015:::The amount of people who didn't even know there was a game on... #AFLSunsCrows:::None
597276706630578177:::Sun May 10 05:47:18 +0000 2015:::You don't realise how much trouble footy in Queensland really is until you're here. Couldn't find one radio staton with #AFLSunsCrows.:::None
597264803166490624:::Sun May 10 05:00:00 +0000 2015:::Inside word from the Gold Coast camp. Ablett not back until round 10. You heard it here first #AFLSunsCrows:::{u'type': u'Point'
